The first thing Stacy Allegro wants you to know: COVID-19 is definitely not just a really bad flu.
The CDC requirements for coronavirus testing were much more stringent at the time, and Allegro didn’t meet the specifications for a test to confirm what all were pretty certain was COVID-19.
Which brings up the second thing Allegro wants you to know: Healthy people are getting this, and some are dying.
